Language: C++

*******************************************************************
Intructions to compile and execute code:

1. To compile, type ''make'' at the terminal (without the quotes).
2. To execute, follow the following format ./cipher <CIPHER NAME> <KEY> <ENC/DEC> <INPUTFILE> <OUTPUT FILE>

*******************************************************************
Cipher Available :
 - DES: Data Encryption Standard
 - AES: Advanced Encryption Standard
 
Mode Available:
 - ENC: Encryption
 - DEC: Decryption
 
Note: We did not implemented the extra credit cipher.